GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE BILL 242
Short Title: H.A.L.L. Accountability Act. (Public)
Sponsors: Senators Everitt and Meyer (Primary Sponsors).
Referred to: Rules and Operations of the Senate
March 6, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO MAKE REDISTRICTING DOCUMENTS PUBLIC RECORDS BY ENACTING
3 THE HOLD ALL LEGISLATORS LIABLE (H.A.L.L.) ACCOUNTABILITY ACT.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. Section 27.7(d) of S.L. 2023-134 is repealed.
6 SECTION 2. This act is effective when it becomes law.
